sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as Upstream Query
    participant S as ThalamusService
    participant P as Planner
    participant RC as Runtime Config
    participant D as DAG Executor
    participant CE as CortexExecutor
    participant SK as Skill (.md)
    participant Ports as Data / Source / Web Ports
    participant LLM as LLM Transport
    participant Ref as Reflexion
    participant KG as Knowledge Graph

    U->>S: runCycle({query, dag?, daemonJob?, cortices?})
    S->>P: resolve DAG source
    P->>RC: planner + cortex filters
    RC-->>P: forced / disabled / overrides
    P-->>S: finalized DAGPlan

    S->>D: execute(plan, cycleId)
    D->>D: validate names, deps, cycles
    D->>CE: execute level in parallel
    CE->>SK: load selected skill
    CE->>RC: per-cortex overrides
    CE->>Ports: helper data + structured sources + optional web
    CE->>LLM: analyze sanitized payload
    LLM-->>CE: CortexOutput
    CE-->>D: findings + metadata
    D-->>S: pass result

    S->>Ref: evaluate gaps / stop criteria
    Ref-->>S: stop or replan

    S->>KG: persist confidence-kept findings
    KG-->>S: research_cycle_finding links + edges
    S-->>U: cycle result
